'''''Thamizhan''''' (: ''Tamilian'') () is a   directed by Ravichandran. The film stars , , ,  and . The film's score and soundtrack are composed by D.Imman.  The film was released for Tamil  New Year.It is written by director Ravichandran and distributed by London based Tamil language telechannel â€“ Cee I TV.
The film was made on an extremely high budget but the movie was average grosser  but it is still considered as one of the actor's best movie due to the stoyline
Surya (Vijay) is a lawyer with right values, who tries to redress things the legal way.He madly falls in love with Priya(Priyanka Chopra). His brother-in-law Shakthivel (Nasser), also an upright lawyer, is killed in the process of upholding justice. Surya's sister (Revathy) also meets a pitiful end at the hands of criminals. But Surya refuses to give up. His mission is to make the layman understand his legal rights. The hero's trials and triumphs are told with force in ``Thamizhan''.
